			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:03,400",
				"to": "00:14:07,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 843400,
				"to": 847400
			},
			"text": " 100 Ether can be used."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:07,400",
				"to": "00:14:12,080"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 847400,
				"to": 852080
			},
			"text": " As you can see, this contract has many advantages."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:12,080",
				"to": "00:14:15,960"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 852080,
				"to": 855960
			},
			"text": " The owner has full control of the tokens."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:15,960",
				"to": "00:14:20,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 855960,
				"to": 860000
			},
			"text": " Also transparency and knowledge of where their funds go."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:20,000",
				"to": "00:14:26,360"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 860000,
				"to": 866360
			},
			"text": " I want to mention that this contract is also extensible contract via plugins."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:26,360",
				"to": "00:14:32,120"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 866360,
				"to": 872120
			},
			"text": " In these plugins, you cannot specific condition like token allocation when a project is found"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:32,120",
				"to": "00:14:37,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 872120,
				"to": 877400
			},
			"text": " or setting a hard pack for a given project."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:37,400",
				"to": "00:14:44,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 877400,
				"to": 884240
			},
			"text": " The liquid-plagic contract can be used not only for donations, but also for organizations"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:44,240",
				"to": "00:14:45,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 884240,
				"to": 885240
			},
			"text": " management."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:45,240",
				"to": "00:14:51,440"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 885240,
				"to": 891440
			},
			"text": " In an organization, the investors delegate the funds to CEO, the CEO delegates the budget"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:51,440",
				"to": "00:14:56,880"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 891440,
				"to": 896880
			},
			"text": " to the directors, the CTO delegates to the system department and so on."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:14:56,880",
				"to": "00:15:03,520"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 896880,
				"to": 903520
			},
			"text": " And the investors still have full control on where the funds are spent and invested."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:15:03,520",
				"to": "00:15:10,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 903520,
				"to": 910240
			},
			"text": " The same idea applies in fund management where a delegate procomits the Ether to a specific"
		},
