		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:15:46,600",
				"to": "00:15:53,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 946600,
				"to": 953800
			},
			"text": " First, if you need an advanced token contract, consider the minimi contract which has been"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:15:53,800",
				"to": "00:15:56,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 953800,
				"to": 956240
			},
			"text": " fully tested and implemented."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:15:56,240",
				"to": "00:15:59,280"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 956240,
				"to": 959280
			},
			"text": " Second, the yoga token."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:15:59,280",
				"to": "00:16:06,960"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 959280,
				"to": 966960
			},
			"text": " It brings together the features of minimi plus the ERC223 with EIP672."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:16:06,960",
				"to": "00:16:11,960"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 966960,
				"to": 971960
			},
			"text": " This is a powerful token to be considered as a standard for the Ethereum community once"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:16:11,960",
				"to": "00:16:14,640"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 971960,
				"to": 974640
			},
			"text": " the standards are approved."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:16:14,640",
				"to": "00:16:23,440"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 974640,
				"to": 983440
			},
			"text": " And third, the liquid pledging contract could be ideal for many usages."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:16:23,440",
				"to": "00:16:29,720"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 983440,
				"to": 989720
			},
			"text": " It's especially sweeter or blockchain-based donation systems that can make a world a"
		},
